---
import PageLayout from '@layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="ChinaShoe.cc Terms of Service - Read our terms governing the use of our website and services."
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
    { name: 'Terms of Service', url: '/terms/' },
  ]}
>
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">
      Terms of Service
    </h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Last updated: December 2024</p>
  </div>

  <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none">
    <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p>
      By accessing and using ChinaShoe.cc, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provisions of this agreement.
    </p>

    <h2>Description of Service</h2>
    <p>
      ChinaShoe.cc provides a B2B footwear knowledge platform including:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Supplier directory and listings</li>
      <li>Industry encyclopedia and guides</li>
      <li>Market data and analysis</li>
      <li>Design inspiration resources</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>User Responsibilities</h2>
    <p>
      You agree to:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Use the website for lawful purposes only</li>
      <li>Not misuse or attempt to gain unauthorized access</li>
      <li>Provide accurate information when making inquiries</li>
      <li>Respect intellectual property rights</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Supplier Information</h2>
    <p>
      The supplier information on our platform is provided for reference purposes. While we verify supplier credentials, we cannot guarantee the accuracy of all information or the outcome of business relationships formed through our platform.
    </p>

    <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>
      All content on this website, including text, graphics, logos, and images, is the property of ChinaShoe.cc or its content suppliers and protected by intellectual property laws.
    </p>

    <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>
      ChinaShoe.cc shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages resulting from your use or inability to use the service.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
    <p>
      We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to the website.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about these Terms of Service should be sent to <a href="mailto:legal@chinashoe.cc">legal@chinashoe.cc</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
